{"tid":1143173,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【執二攤】湯洛雯頂替黃心穎重拍《法證先鋒IV》","createTime":"2019-05-07T14:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-07T14:21:02.000Z","uid":174654,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"848615889c9cd90d3459acdf11a5ff2af903614a","tid":1143173,"uid":174654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:09:42.000Z","msg":"黃心穎和許志安爆出「安心事件」，二人工作全面叫停，而黃心穎有份演出的劇集，包括《法證先鋒IV》和《牛下女高音》都需要重拍。 日前本報曾報道湯洛雯（靚湯）﹑蔡思貝或黃翠如，都有機會頂替黃心穎在《法證IV》的記者角色，結果由黃心穎的好姊妹靚湯跑出。<br />\n<br />\n有報道指靚湯已落實拍攝《法證IV》，今日她已返無綫試造型，但靚湯要在開工前減磅。另外，有指黃心穎原定今個月要到巴塞隆拿工作，但受「安心事件」影響，要由李佳芯和高海寧頂替。<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190507/s00009/b4349518b67c444bd69035eddf958142.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190507%2Fs00009%2Fb4349518b67c444bd69035eddf958142.jpg&h=34e1f4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190507/1557227590060/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190507%2F1557227590060%2F&d=702bRGgXdrZysJ%2FhnUM8S4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=3e7f4d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190507%2F1557227590060%2F&h=18640f60\" target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190507/1557227590060/</a>"},{"pid":"9a4c1a68e52c2abf6143ebf67c0e738db2173c5d","tid":1143173,"uid":280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:12:15.000Z","msg":"雞穎去死啦"},{"pid":"fb2311fe1e310797f39c27714cdb66f907cdec2b","tid":1143173,"uid":174654,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uWQV8n2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuWQV8n2.gif&h=39e1146f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}